## DRY

| Duplication | Action |
|-------------|--------|
| Same Code in two workflows | `lib/` module or sub-workflow |
| Same HTTP + map sequence | Sub-workflow or custom node |
| Same credential + base URL | Credential type + HTTP Request node defaults |
| Same Switch rules | Switch node with shared expressions or lib helper |

If you copy-paste more than two lines of logic between workflows, extract.

