## Credentials and secrets

| Rule | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Never in git | No API keys, tokens, passwords in workflow JSON, Code, or vault |
| Credential store | Values only in n8n credential UI / secret manager |
| Export hygiene | Strip `credentials` object IDs before commit or use env-specific imports |
| Sandbox | Mock, httpbin, local files — document in [[credentials/catalog]] |
| Custom credential types | `ICredentialType` + test request; document fields, not values |

