## Comments

| Use for | Not for |
|---------|---------|
| n8n item/binary quirks | Restating Set node field list |
| Why sub-workflow vs inline | Commented-out nodes (delete them) |
| Link to vault ADR | Credential values |

**Sticky notes + vault** = workflow narrative. **JSDoc/TSDoc** = `lib/` and package API.

